      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "+, Ths lumber workers were organized\nlast week under the A. l.. u. by A. c..\nWilliams. They will meet every\nTuesday evening at Central Labor\nhall. Two hundred and fifty men\nare eligible to membership and it is\nexpected that this number will great\nly increase by the opening of spring.\nThe new union was launched last\nSaturday. c. A. Gray was elected\npresident and c. T. Cook secretary."
    }
